public class BoundedSortedMap<K,V>
extends TreeMap<K,V>

A Map implementation that grows to a fixed size and then retains only a fixed number of the highest (largest) keys. All keys used in this class must implements Comparable.

See Also:
BoundedSortedMultiMap, Serialized Form
